    "description": "PRstage F400Z is a professional LED spotlight with a high color rendering index of RA>95, delivering natural and vibrant colors on any stage.\nIt supports two control modes — 11 and 13 CH, making it a versatile solution for various applications.\nKey features include:\nLamp reset via menu or console,\nSmooth 0–100% dimming,\nConstant current drive for stable operation,\nIntelligent power adjustment based on temperature sensor,\nAutomatic fan speed control.\nPRstage F400Z is perfect for concerts, bars, and theater stages where not only power but flawless color reproduction is essential.",
